{"data": [{"id": "4745286", "title": "Wall Street Breakfast Podcast: Stock Futures Stabilize After Sharp Selloff", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Graph\" data-id=\"182207581\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ewg3D</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <p><span>Listen below or on the go on </span><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502?mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apple Podcasts</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx?si=r3_yJgxiQiivJwNQG8WNew&amp;nd=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a></p> <p><div class=\"pcast hidden-print\">\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-1\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"pcast__top-img pcast__marketing\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2018/11/21/podcast_series_header.png\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-2\"><iframe src=\"https://widget.spreaker.com/player?episode_id=63390701&amp;theme=light&amp;playlist=false&amp;playlist-continuous=false&amp;chapters-image=true&amp;episode_image_position=right&amp;hide-logo=true&amp;hide-likes=true&amp;hide-comments=true&amp;hide-sharing=true&amp;hide-download=true&amp;color=ff6900\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200px\" frameborder=\"0\" sap-id=\"4\"></iframe></div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-3\">\n    <div class=\"pcast__ad-container\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</p> <p>Our major stories today: U.S. stock futures stabilize after sharp selloff (0:28). Will Amazon <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387951-amazon-could-face-strike-in-us-during-busy-holiday-season\" rel=\"noopener\">strike</a> during busy holiday season? (2:15) Micron shares slump 16% (3:45).</p> <p>U.S. stock futures <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387980-sp500-nasdaq-dow-jones-outlook-stock-market\">stabilized</a> on Thursday after a sharp selloff on Wall Street the previous day, triggered by the Federal Reserve's revised outlook for interest rates in 2025: Dow +0.10%; S&amp;P 500 -0.03%; Nasdaq -0.17%.</p> <p>Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) fell below the $100,000 mark on Thursday, retreating sharply from recent all-time highs following signals from the US Federal Reserve of fewer interest rate cuts in 2025.</p> <p>Stock futures ticked up slightly, rebounding from the previous session\u2019s losses, as the Federal Reserve forecasted persistent inflation and limited rate cuts in 2025, as <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745152-wall-street-lunch-fed-cuts-rates\">discussed</a> in-depth on yesterday's Wall Street Lunch. The outlook followed a widely expected quarter-point rate reduction by the central bank.</p> <p>In the bond market, the U.S. 10-year Treasury yield is up 2 basis points to 4.52%.</p> <p>Central banks in Europe will <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387957-european-markets-in-red-tracking-stock-sell-off-in-asia-and-the-us-boe-decision-in-focus\">decide</a> on monetary policy today, including the Bank of England, which is expected to hold borrowing costs steady, balancing persistent inflation concerns against indications of slowing growth.</p> <p>Asia-Pacific markets traded in red on Thursday, tracking the fall sell-off on Wall Street overnight. Investors assessed the Bank of Japan\u2019s decision to keep its policy rate unchanged at 0.25% for the third straight meeting<strong>. </strong></p> <p>Meanwhile, caution mounted ahead of Friday's decision on key lending rates from the Chinese central bank.</p> <p>The <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/USD:JPY#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">Japanese yen</a> fell past 155 per dollar on Thursday, reaching a one-month low, after the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387949-bank-of-japan-keeps-policy-rate-unchanged-at-025-as-widely-expected\">Bank of Japan left its policy rate unchanged at 0.25%, as widely expected</a>.</p> <p>Investors are now focused on BOJ Governor Kazuo Ueda\u2019s post-meeting press conference for insights into the timing of future rate hikes.</p> <p>The Teamsters\u2014a labor union group\u2014<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387951-amazon-could-face-strike-in-us-during-busy-holiday-season\">said</a> that Amazon (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a>) will face its largest strike in U.S., starting Thursday, amidst a busy holiday season.</p> <p>The workers are demanding better wages and working conditions amid claims that the retailer failed to negotiate effectively with the union. Workers at the facility said a union contract should include minimum pay of $30 per hour and better safety protections.</p> <p>\u201cIf your package is delayed during the holidays, you can blame Amazon\u2019s insatiable greed. We gave Amazon a clear deadline to come to the table and do right by our members. They ignored it,\u201d said Teamsters General President Sean M. O\u2019Brien.</p> <p>The Teamsters said that the strike will impact several major cities, including New York City, Atlanta, San Francisco, and Skokie, Illinois. Workers from multiple facilities will join picket lines.</p> <p>An Amazon spokesperson <a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/Business/teamsters-announces-nationwide-strike-amazon-begin-thursday/story?id=116931631\" rel=\"nofollow\">told</a> <em>ABC </em>News, however, that \"For more than a year now, the Teamsters have continued to intentionally mislead the public claiming that they represent 'thousands of Amazon employees and drivers.' They don't, and this is another attempt to push a false narrative,\" adding that the Teamsters have illegally coerced workers to join the union.</p> <p>The spokesperson added that the company has increased the minimum starting wage by 20% for workers in fulfillment centers and for transportation, and in September increased the average base wage to $22 per hour.</p> <p>The retailer has garnered a 47% share price gain this year, and its stock price is marginally higher, up 0.39%, to $221.38 per share during after-hours trading on Wednesday.</p> <p>Micron Technology (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a>) shares <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387979-biggest-stock-movers-thursday-mu-meso-and-more\">slumped</a> 16% despite surpassing FQ1 expectations, as its FQ2 guidance disappointed investors.</p> <p>The company projects adjusted earnings of $1.33\u2013$1.53 per share, falling short of the $1.93 consensus, and revenue of $7.7B\u2013$8.1B, with the midpoint trailing the $8.99B estimate. Adjusted gross margin for the quarter is expected to fall between 37.5% and 39.5%, below the consensus of 41.3%.</p> <p>CEO Sanjay Mehrotra remained optimistic, stating, \"While consumer-oriented markets are weaker in the near term, we expect growth to resume in the second half of our fiscal year. We are gaining share in high-margin, strategic market segments and are well-positioned to capitalize on AI-driven growth, creating significant value for stakeholders.\"</p> <p>Western Digital (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WDC\" title=\"Western Digital Corporation\">WDC</a>) and Seagate (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STX\" title=\"Seagate Technology Holdings plc\">STX</a>), which often trade in tandem with Micron, fell following the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745194-micron-technology-inc-mu-post-earnings-q1-2025-earnings-call-transcript\">results</a>.</p> <p>Seeking Alpha analyst <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/kumquat-research#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">Kumquat Research</a> said the company was dealt a \"significant blow\" as evidenced by its Q2 outlook and Q1 results, due in part to slowing output from the enterprise.</p> <p>The Biden administration has <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387955-epa-california-ban-new-gas-powered-car-sales\">granted</a> California permission to ban the sale of new gas-powered vehicles by 2035, enacting a major climate policy before the end of its term in January that will likely be revoked by president-elect Donald Trump.</p> <p>On the economic calendar, look for Initial Jobless Claims at 8:30 AM. The number of individuals filing for unemployment benefits in the U.S. is expected to fall to 232K from 242K.</p><div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p>Editor's Note: This article covers one or more microcap stocks. Please be aware of the risks associated with these stocks.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182207581/image_182207581.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745286-us-stock-futures-stabilize-after-sharp-selloff", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 14:20:00"}, {"id": "4745219", "title": "The Fed's Hawkish Pivot Signals Big Trouble Ahead For Markets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell Speaks At The 2023 Centennial Conference\" data-id=\"1782089362\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Chip Somodevilla</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As expected, the Fed cut its overnight interest by 25 bps on December 18. However, the dot plot showed a more hawkish policy path in 2025 than expected, so the Fed swaps market is now only pricing in one rate cut.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1782089362/image_1782089362.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745219-fed-hawkish-pivot-signals-big-trouble-ahead-for-markets", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 14:15:00"}, {"id": "4745271", "title": "Mesa Laboratories: GKE Acquisition New Crown Jewel, Still Doesn't Move The Needle", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Update</h2> <p>Since <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4630702-mesa-laboratories-stock-continued-pressure-on-equity-re-rating-reiterate-hold\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4630702-mesa-laboratories-stock-continued-pressure-on-equity-re-rating-reiterate-hold\" target=\"_blank\">my last publication</a> on Mesa Laboratories, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MLAB\" title=\"Mesa Laboratories, Inc.\">MLAB</a></span>) in August '23 the stock has pushed sideways into congestion and is -6% in the red. MLAB shares haven't recovered to pandemic-era highs, and my extensive coverage on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745271-mesa-laboratories-gke-acquisition-new-crown-jewel", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 14:05:57"}, {"id": "4745246", "title": "Rates Spark: Long-End Rates Look Too Low Post The FOMC", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lower Interest Rates\" data-id=\"2173183083\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DNY59/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/padhraic-garvey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Padhraic Garvey, CFA</a>, <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/michiel-tukker/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michiel Tukker</a>, <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"noopener\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2><span>The recalibrated market discount for the funds rate exposes the 10yr rate as still too low here</span></h2> <p>The 25bp cut from the FOMC was expected, but the big</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745246-rates-spark-long-end-rates-look-too-low-post-fomc", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 12:33:00"}, {"id": "4745243", "title": "Ripple: RLUSD Stablecoin And Its Impact On XRP In The Crypto Bull Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold ripple stacked on a bright background of business graphics close-up. Ripple crypto-currency. Anonymous. Virtual currency\" data-id=\"1135927483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Larina Marina</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ripple USD (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XRP-USD\" title=\"Ripple USD\">XRP-USD</a>) has been all the rage since the crypto market got into a bull trajectory, following President Trump's election win and his pro-crypto stance during the campaign. One crypto company to potentially benefit from possible policy</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745243-ripple-rlusd-stablecoin-impact-on-xrp-crypto-bull-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 12:14:42"}, {"id": "4745238", "title": "Apple: Insourcing Can Structurally Lift Gross Margins", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Girl is runing on the city stairs and listening the music\" data-id=\"825721894\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1040px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">praetorianphoto/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Performance Assessment</span></h2> <p>Apple (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AAPL\" title=\"Apple Inc.\">AAPL</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://see